# A solid block of more or less pure metal, often but not necessarily [[brick]]like in shape and [[trapezoidal]] in cross-section, the result of pouring out and cooling molten metal, often immediately after [[smelting]] from raw [[ore]] or [[alloy|alloying]] from constituents.

